Class ShapeBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.gnwi.mfsim.model.graphics.shape.ShapeBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ShapeInterface

    public class ShapeBox
extends java.lang.Object
implements ShapeInterface
    This class represents a 2D box. The box is defined by its side lengths x an y.
